Author: lazyobsessive
Text: This happened to me in high school. One of my friends (not close by any means) told me that there were a lot of rumors going around about me saying I was anorexic. Multiple teachers and peers asked me about it... it sucked. The worst part of it all was when other parents told my parents, my parents laughed and did nothing to help me.  I feel for you, remember that you won’t remember most of the people in high school on a few years. Other people’s perspectives have no bearing on material outcomes!
